        <h1>Beginner’s Guide to Nootropics</h1>
        <p class="lead">Start smarter—not stronger. Learn the basics, personalize a safe starting stack, and feel more focused with fewer unknowns.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="#quick-start" class="btn btn--primary">Build My Starter Stack</a>
          <a href="#tldr" class="btn btn--secondary">See the 60‑Second Summary</a>
          <a href="#starter-stacks" class="btn btn--text">Prefer caffeine‑free?</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="trust-strip">
          <li><strong>5,763+ orders</strong> shipped to 17 countries</li>
          <li><strong>4‑hour</strong> Dubai delivery; UAE same/next day</li>
          <li><strong>Free international express</strong> on 300 AED+ | Easy 3‑day refunds</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="ai-widget" data-component="ask-the-guide" aria-label="Ask the Guide (placeholder)">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Ask the Guide… e.g., Build a caffeine‑free stack" aria-label="Ask the Guide">
          <div class="prompt-chips">
            <button type="button">Focus at work?</button>
            <button type="button">Caffeine‑free stack</button>
            <button type="button">Compare Alpha‑GPC vs CDP</button>
            <button type="button">Is Phenibut okay for beginners?</button>
