        <h2>How to choose</h2>
        <ol class="numbered">
          <li>Pick your primary goal (Focus, Calm, Memory, Energy)</li>
          <li>Choose caffeine‑friendly or caffeine‑free</li>
          <li>Note sensitivities (stimulants, sleep)</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="matrix-note banner banner--warn">
          Some compounds (e.g., Phenylpiracetam, Phenibut) are not beginner daily tools.
        </div>
        <div class="ai-quiz" data-component="guided-quiz">
          <button class="btn btn--primary">Personalize my plan (AI)</button>
        </div>
      </section>

